commit.message: Use raw strings for regular expressions passed to south.
Fix bugfix in color parsing for tint.
Use stock lru_cache instead of provided one.
Add six as a dependency instaed of using django provided one, because django 3 doesn't include it.
Bugfix: pass request instead of session to image_url on img tag.
Bugfix: expect request object instead of session object for prerendring images.
Simplify working with image urls out of templates.
Allow working with no request when using autogen.
Provide a function to simplify creating an image url.
Using a minfest based storage was a bad idea. file uniqueness cannot be handled by the image storage: it must be handled by the corresponding media storage or static storage.
Fix alpha channel when applyinf overlays.
Implement the same technique that ManifestStaticFilesStorage uses in order to allow for very future cache expiration and to prevent issues with strict caching policy in chrome.
Do not reuse variable with different type.
